        <title>🎶 Uncanny — Action Rhythm Boss Game</title>
        <published>2023-04-18T00:00:00+00:00</published>
        <updated>2023-04-18T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
        
        <author>
          <name>
            
              Marcus Aas Jensen
            
          </name>
        </author>
        
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://marcusaasjensen.com/portfolio/uncanny/"/>
        <id>https://marcusaasjensen.com/portfolio/uncanny/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://marcusaasjensen.com/portfolio/uncanny/">&lt;p&gt;✨ &lt;strong&gt;Uncanny&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; is a fast-paced &lt;strong&gt;action rhythm game&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; where you dodge and dash through surreal boss attacks.&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
Blending rhythm-based mechanics with bullet-hell chaos, it draws inspiration from &lt;em&gt;Just Shapes &amp;amp; Beats&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Cuphead&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; to create a hypnotic, dreamlike challenge.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;iframe frameborder=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;itch.io&#x2F;embed&#x2F;2023586?dark=true&quot; width=&quot;552&quot; height=&quot;167&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;marcusjensen.itch.io&#x2F;uncanny&quot;&gt;Uncanny by Marcus Jensen&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;trophy-highlights&quot;&gt;🏆 Highlights&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎯 Achieved &lt;strong&gt;~100 downloads on itch.io&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🔥 Combines &lt;strong&gt;rhythm gameplay + boss fights&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; in a unique fever-dream style.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎶 Features &lt;strong&gt;original music, animation, and art&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;, all created from scratch.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;bulb-what-players-are-saying&quot;&gt;💡 What Players Are Saying&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Love the characters in it. Feels like a fever dream.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;— &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.youtube.com&#x2F;c&#x2F;Tarodev&quot;&gt;Tarodev&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, Discord&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;camera-flash-gallery&quot;&gt;📸 Gallery&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Screenshot from Uncanny&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;&#x2F;images&#x2F;uncanny-gameplay.png&quot; alt=&quot;Gameplay Screenshot 1&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;tools-development&quot;&gt;🛠️ Development&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Built with:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎮 &lt;strong&gt;Unity&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; for the gameplay in C#&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎧 &lt;strong&gt;FL Studio&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; for the music&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎨 &lt;strong&gt;Krita&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; for the artwork&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🔊 &lt;strong&gt;Audacity&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; for sound editing
All assets were created from scratch (except a few sound effects from &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;freesound.org&quot;&gt;freesound.org&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;).&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;pray-acknowledgements&quot;&gt;🙏 Acknowledgements&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Huge thanks to everyone who played, streamed, and shared feedback during the jam—&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
your input was invaluable in shaping &lt;strong&gt;Uncanny&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; into the hypnotic boss-fight experience it is today. 💜&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
    </entry>
