        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Kita theme support $\LaTeX$ mathematical formulas using &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;katex.org&#x2F;&quot;&gt;KaTeX&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
